	<div class="w-full flex flex-col bg-primary-300 rounded-[48px] px-6 py-[88px]">
		<h2 class="font-dm tracking-wide text-center leading-[37px] lg:leading-[62.50px] text-[30px] lg:text-[50px] w-full lg:max-w-[50%] pb-9 mx-auto">Recuerda tu opinion es la que cuenta</h2>
